        protected long mUpdateDuration
        Duration (in milliseconds) between two updates. This is the inverse of the update rate.

      • mAverage

        protected boolean mAverage
        Whether to form the average over the last duration when reading out sensors. Alternative is to just take the current value.

      • mNextUpdate

        protected long mNextUpdate
        Time of next update required. The time is compared to System.currentTimeMillis().
